message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I am so frustrated with your company! I have been trying to make a claim for weeks, and nothing seems to be moving forward.
I'm deeply sorry to hear about your experience. I understand how frustrating it must be. Before we proceed further, could you please confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for confirming. Could you also provide me with your date of birth, please?
Great, thank you. Lastly, could you confirm the first line of your address and the postcode?

Thank you for completing security. I appreciate your cooperation. I value your feedback and want to help resolve this for you. It sounds like you've been through a tough time. Let's see how we can find a way forward. A possible resolution could be escalating your claim for urgent attention. Would that work for you?
Yes, please do escalate my claim. I need this sorted out as soon as possible.
That's all sorted. I've escalated your claim for urgent attention. I'm glad we could help. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you for your help.
You're welcome! If you have any more concerns in the future, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
